## Results

Implemented a vanilla HTML/CSS/JS web dashboard that uses a WebSocket connection (`/ws/dashboard`) to provide real-time updates of the Chuks AI orchestrator state. The streamer can now view the trigger queue, conversation history, memory statistics, and the live avatar state from a second monitor.

